<br>
Item<br>
Spell/Song<br>
Special bard song (there are 2 (?) that stack with other spell/songs)<br>
<br>
If you have multiple of one type (2 items, 2 songs, etc.), the highest of the hastes wins out (SCHW at 22% beats FBSS at 21%, so you'd have 22%).<br>
<br>
You may see multiple haste spell/song icons, but only the haste from 1 of them (excluding the special bard songs) is doing anything. The others provide some kind of stat adjustment, and you are gaining that from them.<br>
<br>
